===Etymology 1===
{{och-l|傀}} "extraordinary" ({{w|Zhouli}}) > {{och-l|瑰}} "rare, marvelous" > a kind precious stone" ({{w|Shijing}}).

{{och-l|傀|tr=*kûi}} seemingly had the same OC rhyme as {{och-l|怪|tr=*kwrêh; *kwêh}}; they may be merely variants ({{zh-ref|Schuessler, 2007}}).

